Open the code in editor
for backend
install node
in the terminal go for backend directory by the command cd backend
install npm by command npm install
initiate node project by command npm init -y 
download all dependancies by command npm install express passport passport-google-oauth20 postmark dotenv cors cookie-session
create .env file with your client id,secret key ,postmark API
then run backend by command npm start 
for frontend
in the terminal go for frontend directory by the command cd frontend
install npm by command npm install
create react app by command npx create-react-app .
install dependancies npm install axios react-router-dom
then run by command np install
